            Real-time <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-400 to-orange-500">Changefeeds</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            Subscribe to live data changes using WebSockets. Build reactive, real-time applications that update instantly.
          </p>
